# RimWorld Mod ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝสพ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
# ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฦด๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฤผ๏ฟฝฮช .rimworld.config ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝยท๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ

# RimWorld ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝืฐฤฟยผ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๎ฃฉ
# สพ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝSteam ฤฌ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝยท๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
#   Windows: C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\RimWorld
#   Linux:   ~/.steam/steam/steamapps/common/RimWorld
#   macOS:   ~/Library/Application Support/Steam/steamapps/common/RimWorld
RIMWORLD_DIR=YOUR_RIMWORLD_PATH_HERE

# Mod ๏ฟฝฤผ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฦฃ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝัก๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฤฌ๏ฟฝฯฃ๏ฟฝRimTalk-MemoryPatch๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
MOD_FOLDER_NAME=RimTalk-MemoryPatch

# ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฯท๏ฟฝๆฑพ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝัก๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฤฌ๏ฟฝฯฃ๏ฟฝ1.6๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
GAME_VERSION=1.6

# สน๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝหต๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
# 1. ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฦด๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝฤผ๏ฟฝฮช .rimworld.config
# 2. ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ YOUR_RIMWORLD_PATH_HERE ๏ฟฝๆปปฮช๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ RimWorld ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝืฐยท๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ
# 3. ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝรป๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝัก๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ Visual Studio ๏ฟฝิถ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๐ฃฉฃ๏ฟฝ
#    Windows: setx RIMWORLD_DIR "๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝยท๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ"
#    Linux/macOS: export RIMWORLD_DIR="๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝยท๏ฟฝ๏ฟฝ"

English Translation
=====================================================================================
# RimWorld Installation Directory (Required)
# Example Steam default paths:
#   Windows: C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\RimWorld
#   Linux:   ~/.steam/steam/steamapps/common/RimWorld
#   macOS:   ~/Library/Application Support/Steam/steamapps/common/RimWorld
RIMWORLD_DIR=YOUR_RIMWORLD_PATH_HERE

# Mod Folder Name (Optional, Default: RimTalk-MemoryPatch)
MOD_FOLDER_NAME=RimTalk-MemoryPatch

# Game Version (Optional, Default: 1.6)
GAME_VERSION=1.6

# Usage Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to .rimworld.config
# 2. Replace YOUR_RIMWORLD_PATH_HERE with your actual RimWorld installation path
# 3. Environment Variable Setup (Optional, for automatic Visual Studio detection):
#    Windows: setx RIMWORLD_DIR "Your_Path_Here"
#    Linux/macOS: export RIMWORLD_DIR="Your_Path_Here"